Edward Hepple https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Hepple 0 Edward Hepple (4 June 1914 – 3 September 2005), also known and billed as Eddie Hepple, was an Australian actor, voice artist and television scriptwriter, best known for his roles in television serials, soap operas and TV movies. His well-known roles were as Syd Humphrys in Prisoner and the voice of the prospector in the animated series The Silver Brumby.
